values: Kim is a douch-face who doesn't need to read my journal!

Abdominal surgery is no fun.....well, at least I get Vicodin......yeah, anyway, I got my hernia surgery day before yesterday, it being thursday and all. I got it on tuesday.....yeah....sorry, I"m on drugs...lol, I'm ggoing to bed........

I haven't posted in a really long time, huh? I'm still with Kim, 7 months yesterday, I don't know what I'm getting her for valentines...Well, yeah I do, but on the off chance that she reads this before the 14th, I'm not saying shit :P...........What else happened......Kim2 moved in with Kimmy.....They're doing ok.....Kim got a cell phone, and I got a new one....its a picture/video phone...what else.....I'm on my way to graduating...Actually on track for once, shit........I'm quitting smoking..........or trying, at least....Thats a lot of ellipses.....................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................and that fills my ellipse quota for the day!!!!

So, life does take some interesting turns, doesn't it? I dunno........I've been busy the past week. 
      
On Tuesday, I had to keep Kim and Clint from fighting the whole time, and it kinda killed the mood for me and Sarah. It was a lot Clint's fault, but Kimmy's too. I did get a pack that day, too. But I smoked like, 7 of my 15 remaining cigarettes on Wednesday. 
      
On Wednesday, I was supposed to go see Kara, but my mom didn't want to take me to the library, and I was all pissed off, so I went to go see a movie with Kelli. We went to go see "Without a Paddle", and the teller person that sold us our tickets was a friend of mine from 7th grade. It was kinda scary seeing someone from that long ago. He said that I looked different, and I told him he should have seen me a few months ago, when my hair was really long. He looked like himself, but grown up to 16-17. He looked the exact same as he had in seventh grade. The movie was really fuckin funny. I actually LAUGHED in it, and I never laugh out loud in  movies. I dunno......Kelli almost broke up with her boyfriend on Wednesday, though, because he ditched her at the theatres. He was supposed to come, so he could meet me and shit like that. But, he never showed up. Me and Kimmy had a fight on Wednesday, too.....all because I told her the truth about something. 
      
On Thursday.........I don't remember if I did anything.....If I did do anything...wait.....I didn't go to school Thursday, so I was grounded. 
      
On Friday, I just hung out with Kim and Kim and that was fun, we watched 50 First Dates and then, they spent a while getting stuff together for dinner, and then, after dinner, we sat on Kim's (My girlfriend)bed and watched a few Comedy Central stand-ups....Then, after we got done with that, Kim (Friend Kim) took me and Kimmy to my house, so she could go to this other guys' house and see him. Me and Kim went to my room and hung out for about 5 minutes before we boofed. Clint called at the end, which really amused me.....
      
Yesterday, I hung out with Evelyn. That was fun. We talked most of the time. I dunno, I like hanging out with Ev....I hadn't seen her in a while, so it was nice seeing her. She's really matured, like, come to terms with herself, it seems like. She was happy, and I was glad to see that. She looked more alive than she ever has.
      
And today, I'm gonna go hang out with Kim again, where there is a cigarette waiting for me......YAY!!!!!
      
And tomorrow.......................there's school..............................

Ok.....here's a recap on my life since my last post.....ummm........Kara hates me......Sarah's mad at me.......................I'm dating Kim..........Someone's playing Baby-Gestapo on my father-duties.............School's threatening to kick me out.........My dreams and aspirations are slowly fading away, for every day that she doesn't get a freakin pregnancy test........I don't have a cigarette.........I'm still not 18...........my online friends all hate me, because someone, or should I say, 2 SOMEONE'S went on my account and talked shit to all of them..........but somehow, my life is still cool. I really do need a cigarette, though....I'll update later, right now, I'm bored........

YOu know, it's weird when you have one of those moments, one of those revelations, the life-changing realizations. It's moments like these that make us what we are. No, I'm not on drugs and I'm not drunk and, as far as I know, I'm in a sound mental capacity. I'm having all of these realizations, like.........ok, I've spent all of this time trying to figure out what I am, in terms of stereotypes and genres and the such, like, metalhead, goth, punk, and any of the random subdivisions of each. I've come to the conclusion of...WHO THE FUCK CARES?!? IT DOESN'T MATTER AT ALL!!! I'm not goth, and I'm not a hippie and I'm not any of those random things. I'm just me. I'm me. That's the only way I can be explained, is that I'm me. I'm not a whore, or a drug addict or a vampire or a freak. I'm just me. And thats all I need to be. SECOND REVELATION......on suicide: I've come to that conclusion that I really don't want to die. In all honesty, death scares the living shit out of me. I am very against dying, which is amazing considering what I was 8 months ago....hell, what I was 8 weeks ago. I don't want to die. On cutting: with cutting comes the very real possibility of death.....cut too deep and even nick an artery, and it's a very real possibility, not to mention that with cutting comes the lovely and appealing scars! It's like any drug, with enough willpower and support, you can quit. It's not easy, and it's not painless, but, it can happen if you make up your mind, all you have to do is make the choice, someone surprisingly insightful told me that. All I really know, is that I want to be able to wear a muscle shirt and not have to be self conscious about my scars and be able to wear shorts and not worry about, "Are they staring at my cuts?" I figure smoking is self-destructive enough for everything :P.. Revelation 3: My life doesn't suck. I spend all of this time wishing my life was someone else's and I forget that I actually still have a life, that I just have life, in general, that I am alive. It doesn't matter that, oh, the person on TV has such a cool life, oh, they have such an awesome life....Thats my life! I have a cool life, I have an awesome life, I don't have to look at the TV and think, "damn, I wish that was me...", because I don't want to be them...I want to be me!!! I love being me! I have a damn confusing love life, I'm addicted to a lot of things, I don't go to concerts anymore, I don't go to parties anymore.....but I still love being me. I love being alive. And I also plan to change the not going to concerts and not going to parties problems. I don't know, I may sound stoned, but, I really have never been this clear-headed. I have a place in the universe. I'm finally happy. Fo once, lol.

Am I right to be mad at her? I mean, she broke a promise.......am I right? I guess I'm trying to hold on to another piece of my remaining naivete by being so childish.....I miss being childish....I have so little innocence left, I have to hyper-amplify all of my remaining naive moments....I dunno.....I feel really bad for yelling at her, though.....did I overreact? Am I wrong? Should I apologize? Should I not trust her? It was just a small promise about something I did when I was drunk, it's not that big of a deal.............I dunno, I'm confused...............I need a hug............

I dunno, mostly happy now. I met a new person....HOORAY NEW PEOPLE....her name is Sonya, she's cool, and I somehow was telling her about problems I don't tell ANYONE. IT's weird how I opened up with her in about 2 hours. I don't think I've ever done that before. I dunno, bored now, because she went to sleep. I'm thinking about sleeping, but, another hour and a half and it'll be sunrise, so, I dunno, confused, thinking about waiting.....I think I'm gonna go play on her fantabulous Playstation 2! I dunno, I'm retarded!! Grrr..........nicotine withdrawal!!!!!!!!! JOY!!!!!
